"title": "8607: prayer, God's promises concerning",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8607",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God promises to hear and respond to the prayers of his people, when they pray in the name of his Son and according to his will.</p>\n<h2>God expects his people to make requests of him in prayer</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:7-Matt7:11\">MAT 7:7–7:11</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:9-Luke11:13\">LUK 11:9–11:13</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:22\">MAT 21:22</a></p>\n<h2>God promises to answer prayer in the name of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:13-John14:14\">JHN 14:13–14:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:7\">JHN 15:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:16\">JHN 15:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:23-John16:24\">JHN 16:23–16:24</a></p>\n<h2>God promises to respond to the prayers of his people in times of need</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:14-Ps91:16\">PSA 91:14–91:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:14-Ps50:15\">PSA 50:14–50:15</a></p>\n<h2>God promises to hear the prayers of the oppressed</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:17\">PSA 10:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:22-Exod22:23\">EXO 22:22–22:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:26-Exod22:27\">EXO 22:26–22:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:19-Ps102:20\">PSA 102:19–102:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:17\">ISA 41:17</a></p>\n<h2>God promises to hear the prayers of the truly penitent</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:14\">2CH 7:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:37\">EZK 36:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:6\">ZEC 10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech13:8-Zech13:9\">ZEC 13:8–13:9</a></p>\n<h2>God promises to hear the prayers of his obedient people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:22\">1JN 3:22</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The need in prayer to have confidence in God's promises</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:24\">MRK 11:24</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:14\">1JN 5:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:19\">MAT 18:19</a></p>",
